            "title": "Morphology and genetics concur that Anoura carishina is a synonym of Anoura latidens (Chiroptera, Glossophaginae)",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Camilo A.",
                    "lastName": "Calderón-Acevedo"
